s=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛理佢咩mon喇，Vega + freesync mon 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1cea7873837c8bf93a44f3b27d37bc5bddaa42","tid":401163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA GEFORCE GTX 1070 TI 規格曝光！<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/41197/nvidia-geforce-gtx-1070-ti/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnvidia%2F41197%2Fnvidia-geforce-gtx-1070-ti%2F&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=68d5cb03\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/41197/nvidia-geforce-gtx-1070-ti/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前有消息指出NVIDIA將推出GTX 1070 Ti迎擊AMD RX Vega 56，而據最新情報顯示，NVIDIA此回誠意十足，GTX 1070 Ti居然會有多達2432個CUDA核心，亦就是只比GTX 1080少了一組128個，較預期的多了一組。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/21/184705dae8h8ze9dhazhhm.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201709%2F21%2F184705dae8h8ze9dhazhhm.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=9cdd4715&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n時脈方面，GTX 1070 Ti公版將設定為1607MHz起步，亦就是達到了GTX 1080之水準，而加速時脈為1683MHz，相當於GTX 1070，如此算下來整體效能將直逼GTX 1080。而很顯然地，廠商們定會推出超頻版，基本與加速時脈分別超過1700MHz、1800MHz應是輕而易舉之事。<br />\n<br />\n記憶體方面，GTX 1070 Ti將配置8GB GDDR5，時脈8008MHz，沒有用上GDDR5X可能是貨源不充足或是成本偏高。TDP為180W，與GTX 1080一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n發表時間得再等等，GTX 1070 Ti預計將會於11月初推出，價格預計為529美元左右。大家點睇？"},{"pid":"906e0e2f6b133c31a114e2ebf9bf4439b07851c1","tid":401163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>GIGABYTE 疑似在 FB 粉絲團暗示 GEFORCE GTX 1070 TI 相關消息</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201709/21/172332ql8j4ukm8a8al5u7.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201709%2F21%2F172332ql8j4ukm8a8al5u7.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=1f9c231a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.guru3d.com/news-story/gigabyte-teases-geforce-gtx-1070-ti.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.guru3d.com%2Fnews-story%2Fgigabyte-teases-geforce-gtx-1070-ti.html&d=apf0FnxfsF5SIMz8X09L8hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=ffac3235\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.guru3d.com/news-story/gigabyte-teases-geforce-gtx-1070-ti.html</a></div>"},{"pid":"f98615d5d087845038220428a6054505a3e2a3ca","tid":401163,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T07:10:32.000Z","msg":"技姦,怕"},{"pid":"d775858bdbd700a372183baa27d0534fe2952b00","tid":401163,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:13:43.000Z","msg":"根本係1080的gddr5版 順便夾死礦卡"},{"pid":"945d79a062b73bb9a7af0d7e18b123d41b8308ec","tid":401163,"uid":45286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用1070 玩1080p 又overkill<br />\n用1080 玩2k 都係岩岩夠<br />\n<br />\n咁1070ti 玩咩芒??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1070玩1080p overkill得去邊 你咩都開中效就話</blockquote><br />\n我6700+1070用1080p120fps玩war thunder全開都可以v-sync喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcfeacf17013638119013b3bdd60932af2536db8","tid":401163,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:06:58.000Z","msg":"1080都唔撚使529usd 有冇人低能到會去買1070ti咁撚戇鳩呀"}]}